    <h1>Terms of the licence</h1>

    <p class="nhsuk-lede-text">This is a licence for specific Frutiger fonts for NHS organisations only. By registering for this licence, you can get access to authorised versions of the Frutiger font.</p>
    <p>Before you can download and use the Frutiger font under NHS England's licence, you must read and agree to these terms (including the Annex: detailed terms, which you can find a link to within the registration form). As set out at the start of the registration form, by clicking "agree" you confirm that you are authorised to accept these terms (including the detailed terms in the Annex) on behalf of your organisation. Where we refer to "you" or "your" in the rest of these terms, we are therefore referring to your organisation.</p>
    <p>NHS England has a licence for 3 weights of the Frutiger font, which is the brand font for the NHS. Monotype owns the font software and other elements of the font which are protected by intellectual property rights. We call these the "font" in these terms.</p>
    <h2>Who can register for a licence</h2>
